crowdsourced_yara_results.description: Detects Raccoon Stealer 2.0, also referred to as RecordBreaker
crowdsourced_yara_results.author: ditekSHen
Felix Bilstein - yara-signator at cocacoding dot com

sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects modification of the registry settings used for Internet Explorer and other Windows components that use these settings. An attacker can abuse this registry key to add a domain to the trusted sites Zone or insert javascript for persistence

attributes.magic: PE32 executable (GUI) Intel 80386, for MS Windows

threat_severity.level_description: Severity HIGH because it was considered trojan. Other contributing factor was that it could not be run in sandboxes.

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: ET MALWARE Win32/RecordBreaker CnC Checkin M1
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert http $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET any (msg:"ET MALWARE Win32/RecordBreaker CnC Checkin M1"; flow:established,to_server; http.method; content:"POST"; http.header_names; content:!"Referer"; http.request_body; content:"machineId="; fast_pattern; pcre:"/^[a-f0-9]{8}-(?:[a-f0-9]{4}-){3}[a-f0-9]{12}\|/R"; content:"configId="; pcre:"/^[a-f0-9]{32}/R"; reference:md5,f75f596f7a0369717476f304eef7fe9b; classtype:trojan-activity; sid:2036934; rev:2; metadata:affected_product Windows_XP_Vista_7_8_10_Server_32_64_Bit, attack_target Client_Endpoint, created_at 2022_06_08, deployment Perimeter, malware_family RecordBreaker, performance_impact Low, signature_severity Major, updated_at 2022_07_11;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: POLICY-OTHER HTTP request by IPv4 address attempt
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert tcp any any -> any $HTTP_PORTS ( msg:"POLICY-OTHER HTTP request by IPv4 address attempt"; flow:to_server,established; http_header; content:"Host:",fast_pattern,nocase; pcre:"/^Host\x3a\s*(?:(?:25[0-5]|2[0-4][0-9]|[01]?[0-9]?[0-9])\.){3}(?:25[0-5]|2[0-4][0-9]|[01]?[0-9]?[0-9])\s*:?\s*\d*\s*$/ims"; service:http; reference:url,www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec15.html; classtype:policy-violation; sid:50447; rev:1; )
